Description: Provides S4 classes and methods for comprehensive bulk RNA-seq data analysis,
    including differential expression analysis, gene set enrichment analysis (GSEA),
    and gene set variation analysis (GSVA). The package offers a unified framework
    for storing and analyzing bulk RNA-seq data with associated metadata.
